I"Ê<p>Conventions ( Variable Names )</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Variable names need to be lowercase and contain underscores to separate tokens
  Valid: $client_id, $distance
  <em>Invalid</em> : <em>$ORIGIN</em> , <em>$Destination</em> _ <em>Id</em></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Variables should be used across all nodes as though they are in global scope
  This means that:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>do not reuse a variable name for a different purpose</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>e.g., the index variable for generated bid &amp; refill bid shouldnâ€™t have the same name</p>

<p>Valid: $generate_bid_row_index, $refill_bid_row_index</p>

<p><em>Invalid</em>: <em>$index</em> <em>(used for generate and refill)</em></p>
